<HEADLINE>
AS THE WORLD TAKES A NEW LOOK, IT'S THE SAME OLD CUBA
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By LARRY ROHTER   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   MIAMI _ As he traveled from one end of Cuba to another a year
