industry that has been overtaken by cable successes, where better
to find talent? NBC and FOX both figured it out, hiring Scott Sassa
from Turner to lead the way at NBC and plucking Doug Herzog out of
Comedy Central's hands to pump up the volume at FOX. By Keith
