Minnesota Vikings on Sunday to move on to the Super Bowl. Fans in
cities where teams routinely make a run for the NFL championship
might not understand. But for some, like West, a Super Bowl is just
too precious a thing to welcome with just celebratory cheers. (Alan
S. Weiner /New York Times Photo)
