<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-18 21:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8264 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BEAUTY-BAR-375&AMP;ADD-SF     01-18 0847
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BEAUTY-BAR-375&AMP;ADD-SFCHRON </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A MANICURE WITH A BEER CHASER 
</HEADLINE>
   (Eds: This story also moved in the ``a'' national news file)  
 By NEVA CHONIN  
 c.1999, San Francisco Chronicle  
<TEXT>
