<HEADLINE>
GOLFER NICKLAUS SLATED FOR HIP REPLACEMENT 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By JIM MCCABE  
 c.1999 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOSTON _ Jack Nicklaus will be in Boston next week, but it will
be medical business, not golfing pleasure.
</P>
