especially since his record of playing in the majors ended at 146
when he did not take part in last summer's British Open or PGA
Championship.
</P>
<P>
   His 1998 season was unspectacular, soured by the hip problems.
Though he stirred fans' emotions last April when he became the
oldest player, at 58, to ever finish in the top 10 at the Masters,
Nicklaus did not take part in any tournament after the US Senior
Open in July.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
