<HEADLINE>
SOSA SKIPS A DINNER THAT WAS TO HONOR HIM 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Ill., Nev., Calif.) (DUPLICATION NOTICE: Also filed in category ``a'') (nk) 
